Wasn't even fed, 8/5 with 5 items.....{{sticker:sg-lux-2}}

Vayne is OP ONCE she completes her items. She's like Yi, she's nearly impossible to deal with in the late game. That is what a hyper carry is. When she's building crit with the same attack speed is when she is a problem, because she power spikes earlier and Vayne has one of the highest base attack speeds in the game. The win conditions vs on-hit Vayne are: don't let her reach late game. You messed up.

At this point you would have to get a pick on her. and end before she managed to respawn, or hope to god you got another pick on her when she did.
